@@TJvListView.AutoClipboardCopy
Summary
  Indicates whether the current selected item is automatically copied to the clipboard when the user
  copis.
Description
  Set AutoClipboardCopy to true to have th eselected item automatically copied to the clipbaord when
  the presses the default copy shortcut (Ctrl+C).

