@@TJvListView.HeaderImages
Summary
  Sets the images used for headers.
Description
  Assign an existing TImagelist to this property to specify the images to draw on the column headers.
  You also need to set the ImageIndex of individual column headers to display the images.
Note
  Due to a limitation of the header control its height is fixed. Always use images that fit within the
  fixed height of the header.

